time to reduce their dependency on tobacco and find other sponsors.
</P>
<P>
However, he also admitted a sponsorship ban would affect
international events such as the British Grand Prix.
</P>
<P>
Many tobacco firms, long-time sponsor of variety of
high-profile sports events, showed their disappointment at the
news. 
