<HEADLINE> Results of Cameroun's Parliamentary ELections to </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YAOUNDE, May 18 (Xinhua) -- Results of the parliamentary
elections in Cameroun will be made public in 20 days, according
to local radio reports today.
</P>
<P>
About 3.5 million Camerounians voted Saturday in 16010 polling
stations nationwide to elect parliamentarians for the 180 seats
